T5102."shinseishoKanriNo"=X5201."shinseishoKanriNo" LEFT JOIN (SELECT * FROM ( SELECT T5202."shinseishoKanriNo", T5202."ninteichosaJisshiYMD", row_number() over(PARTITION BY T5202."shinseishoKanriNo" X5202 ON T5102."shinseishoKanriNo"=X5202."shinseishoKanriNo" LEFT JOIN (SELECT * FROM ( SELECT T5301."shinseishoKanriNo", T5301."ikenshoSakuseiIraiYMD", row_number() over(PARTITION BY ) X5301 ON T5102."shinseishoKanriNo"=X5301."shinseishoKanriNo" LEFT JOIN (SELECT * FROM ( SELECT T5302."shinseishoKanriNo", T5302."ikenshoJuryoYMD", row_number() over(PARTITION BY
